# Optional. If set, the site will pre-fill OpenRouter as a backend choice
# without prompting visitors to paste a key. The first-visit modal still
# appears once so the user can pick Local vs Remote.
#
# IMPORTANT: this value is baked into the production JS bundle at build
# time and is therefore visible to anyone who loads the deployed site.
# For the demo deploy we recommend creating a dedicated OpenRouter key
# with a low monthly spending limit, OR rely on the :free tier of
# google/gemma-4-31b-it which is rate-limited but costs nothing.
#
# Get a key at https://openrouter.ai/keys
VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
